Duke Dennis is a popular American content creator and YouTube gamer. He became famous after uploading content about the basketball video game NBA 2K17 on his YouTube channel. His videos attract millions of subscribers and have earned him a reasonable fortune.

Who is Duke Dennis?

Duke Dennis is an American gaming YouTuber and content creator.

What is Duke Dennis famous for?

Many know Duke Dennis from his YouTube gaming content. His first viral basketball video game was about NBA 2K17. The video attracted millions to his YouTube channel. Since then, Duke's channels and fame have been growing by the day.

What is Duke Dennis' real name?

The YouTuber's birth name is Duke Dennis. Most fans know him as Duke and assume it is a nickname or moniker.

Where is Duke Dennis from?

Duke Dennis' hometown is in Georgia, Alabama, USA. He was born and raised there.

How old is Duke Dennis?

Duke Dennis' age is 29 years as of 2024. The acclaimed YouTuber is an American national of mixed ethnicity.

What is Duke Dennis' birthday?

The American YouTuber was born on 26 February 1994.

Who is Duke Dennis' brother?

Dennis' two younger brothers appeared in a July 2019 video on his YouTube channel. One of them is named Darius.

Where does Duke Dennis live?

Duke currently resides in the City Heights in San Diego, California. Before this, he lived with one of his brothers in South Carolina, USA.

Has Duke Dennis been in the military?

Dennis served in the USA army. He was deployed to Germany after completing basic training and AIT.

YouTube career

Dennis has always been passionate about basketball since childhood. The YouTuber is an incredible player on the pitch and with basketball video games.

His career as a streamer began in 2013 when he created a YouTube channel and uploaded a series of content about basketball simulation video games called NBA 2K.

His first video was NBA 2K17 dropped 19 on superstar head â€“ best jumpshot in NBA 2K17. He followed it up with a second one, Angry Trash Talker, which also had a positive reception.

Today, Duke runs three channels, a Twitch account, and also posts videos on TikTok.

Is Duke Dennis a millionaire?

Duke Dennis' net worth ranges between $1 million and $5 million. He makes money from YouTube and also sells his merch on the website Design by Humans.

Duke Dennis' YouTube channel,@DukeDennis864, creates a steady income. It has 1.9 million followers and over 179 million views as of 2024.

His second channel, @DukeDennisAMP (created in 2020), has 1.94 million subscribers and more than 106 million views. The third one, @DukeDennisLive (created in 2021), has 626k subscribers and over 65 million views as of 2024. Brands also pay him to advertise them in his videos.

Duke Dennis' jeeps

Duke Dennis has bought three Jeep Wranglers and even has a Twitter account, @dukedennisjeep, for his cars. He purchased the first one, a camo Jeep Wrangler with a D-block interior, in 2017 and gave it to his brother after buying a Jeep Wrangler with a Scat pack engine. He now owns an SRT Jeep Wrangler.

Duke said he saw many jeeps growing up in South Carolina and fell in love with them. He plans to buy a luxury car in the future. He said it might be a G-wagon, Lamborghini, or whatever brand he decides on.

Was Duke Dennis' house robbed?

Duke posted footage on social media showing two men breaking into his home in 2020 while he was streaming the NBA 2K21 game. Some alleged it was a fake robbery until he shared his thoughts about the experience on social media.

Duke Dennis' criminal allegations

Duke Dennis' mugshot image that went viral on social media towards the middle of 2021 forced him to clear the air.

Was Duke Dennis jailed?

Duke was only locked in police custody for a while and set free. The NBA YouTuber admitted that he broke the law, but that was when he was still in high school. He also stated that he never did anything that would have made him serve a jail sentence.

Duke Dennis' charges are unknown to the public. Reports claim it is linked to his days in the US Army before he became a full-time gaming streamer.

How did Duke Dennis get his dreads?

A twisting with gel method was used to install dreadlocks on Duke's 4B hair type, which is dense and compact. The locks have become tight and puffy with time. Multiple content creators have made videos about installing Duke Dennis' dreads.

Who is Duke Dennis' girlfriend?

It is unclear whether Duke Dennis is dating because he keeps his love life low-key. Nevertheless, fans know the YouTuber has been in at least one relationship because he once interviewed his ex-girlfriend, Kali, on his channel.

How many kids does Duke Dennis have?

Sources claim he has six children, who he keeps out of the limelight. The rumor about Duke Dennis' children has been going on for a long time, but he is yet to respond to these claims.

How tall is Duke Dennis?

Duke Dennis' height is 6 feet 2 inches (187.96 cm).

Duke Dennis' meme

Dennis went viral on TitTok because of videos about his unspoken rizz meme. In the videos, he is seen checking out a young lady. He makes hand signals to her and follows her for a conversation.

Dennis has been playing computer games since he was a kid.

He has participated in online competitions since childhood.

Duke has three YouTube channels.

He has two younger brothers and sometimes features his siblings in his videos.

He is a friendly person with an easy-going personality.

His funny nature makes his YouTube videos enjoyable to watch.

Dennis is a big fan of actor Ryan Reynolds

Duke loves tattoos and has some on his arms and chest.

Duke Dennis keeps his private life secret from the media. The YouTuber often posts videos of himself driving luxurious cars alone or with friends and playing basketball on social media.
